    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "the `--keystore` is a global flag, if you place it _after_ the `console` command it's interepreted as a `local` flag, which causes it to be ignored. As @karalabe pointed out, the proper test would be \r\n\r\n* `./geth --keystore \"/usr/local/eth/wallets\" --testnet --rpcapi admin,eth,miner,personal,web3 console`\r\n* `./geth --testnet --rpcapi admin,eth,miner,personal,web3 --keystore \"/usr/local/eth/wallets\" console`\r\n\r\nClosing this, please reopen if I misunderstood something and there's some bug I missed",
